							"parentStyle": false,
							"left": 624,
							"top": 240,
							"width": 277.22998046875,
							"height": 70,
							"text": "SortedMap集合的key存储的特点：\n首先是无序不可重复的，另外放在SortedMap\n集合key部分的元素会自动按照大小顺序排序，\n称为可排序的集合"
						},
						{
							"_type": "UMLNoteLinkView",
							"_id": "AAAAAAGeLz8Rj2IjdK4=",
							"_parent": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGeIQOKqmBEm6U="
							},
							"font": "Arial;13;0",
							"parentStyle": false,
							"head": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGeLzUmi2E1/3M="
							},
							"tail": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGeLz5WaGIf5+4="
